  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that the use of a combination of Atropine and Remifentanil will
      safely facilitate non emergent intubation procedure as effectively as the protocol of
      Atropine, Fentanyl, and Succinylcholine.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
